FT.

Goal St Albans - Jeffers gets his hat-trick after being initially denied by Ejeheri.

3-0 ⚪️ 90+7' #TheClarets

Jeffers fires over from a St Albans counter-attack. Good defending from James, mind you.

2-0 ⚪️ 90+5' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Just isn't falling for us again as Esan's shot is parried by Berry, and Blackwell just can't connect with the follow-up before the hosts clear.

6 minutes added on.

Blackwell picks out Esan in the box, as the striker blazes over with a shot on the turn.

2-0 ⚪️ 86' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

St Albans should be down to 10 there as Lodovica rounds Berry outside the box, and gets taken out by the Saints 'keeper who was the last man. Escapes with a booking...

Lodovica then heads over from the free-kick.

2-0 ⚪️ 84' #TheClarets

Lodovica heads over from Blackwell's cross - good chance.

2-0 ⚪️ 78' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Today's attendance is 1,018. Thank you, as always, to our travelling support.

2-0 ⚪️ 77' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Close to a third as Weiss fires narrowly wide in the box.

2-0 ⚪️ 74' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Goal St Albans. Jeffers again as he rifles home from a dangerous looking free-kick.

2-0 ⚪️ 71' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Second change.

1-0 ⚪️ 64' #TheClarets https://t.co/0CZMpJ9nZg

SAVE EJEHERI! The 'keeper spreads out to deny Jeffers in the box.

1-0 ⚪️ 59' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

We're forced into our first change.

We're all with you, Louis! Wishing you a speedy recovery ❤️

1-0 ⚪️ 53' #TheClarets https://t.co/ue1eGAae7i
We've see a replay and it looks like Louis has turned his ankle whilst shielding the ball. Definitely cannot continue today.
Stretcher is on. This looks serious....

Early pause in play as Dunne has gone down from a coming together - looks to be in some discomfort...

1-0 ⚪️ 48' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Back underway for the second-half. Come on, you Clarets!!

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻
HT | Behind at the break.

1 minute added on.

1-0 ⚪️ 45' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Goal St Albans. Jeffers steps up and sends Ejeheri the wrong way to put the Saints in the lead.

1-0 ⚪️ 41' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Penalty for St Albans as Jeffers goes down in the box following very minimal contact from Vaz. Harsh.

0-0 ⚪️ 40' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE! Yila rises the highest in the Saints box and beats Berry to the ball in the air, heading narrowly wide!

0-0 ⚪️ 30' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

First real chance for a while as Weiss takes aim at goal, but Ejeheri is there to make a calm save.

0-0 ⚪️ 29' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Weiss slips in Jeffers nicely for a shot in the box, but he scuffs his effort straight at Ejeheri.

0-0 ⚪️ 19' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE AGAIN! City creating some good early chances as Trotter's volley from outside the box is deflected just wide!

Corner kick for the Clarets that eventually comes to nothing.

0-0 ⚪️ 8' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE! Blackwell is played in behind with a ball over the top of the St Albans defence, as the attacker fires into the side netting!

0-0 ⚪️ 6' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

City respond in kind as Blackwell wiggles his way into the St Albans box, and gets a deflected shot away that is saved by Berry.

0-0 ⚪️ 5' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Early chance for the hosts as Jeffers fires over first-time following a smar short corner from Weiss.

0-0 ⚪️ 4' #TheClarets

Blackwell fires over from a dangerous City free-kick.

908 is tonight's attendance.

2-1 ⚪️ 90+7' #TheClarets

BLACKERS!!! GAME ON!

2-1 ⚪️ 90+5' #TheClarets https://t.co/GyTpgnpFia

Final change.

2-0 ⚪️ 90+'2 #TheClarets https://t.co/1w11hDWIpM

10 minute are added on. 

2-0 ⚪️ 90' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Goal for Dulwich. The hosts block a clearance in the City box, before Clarke gets his second of the game.

2-0 ⚪️ 87' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Play is resumed... then Vaz gets a second yellow for a late challenge on Clarke. City now down to 9 men.

1-0 ⚪️ 84' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻
@robertpattie61 Dulwich's Clarke grabbed Vaz in a headlock from a throw-in.

We *think* both managers have been sent off too... we may be able to continue a game of football soon once the referee finishes taking his time.... 

1-0 ⚪️ 83' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Red cards for both sides. Yila for Chelmsford, not sure who got sent off for Dulwich...

Vaz & Trotter also receive a yellows, alongside Clarke and Ming... it's hard to report on what's going on...

1-0 ⚪️ 81' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Just as it seemed to be calming down, a player on the Dulwich bench starts it all over again towards the City bench...

1-0 ⚪️ 78' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Pause in play as a big scrap kicks off following Dulwich's Clarke grabbing Vaz in a headlock.

Referee has some thinking to do.

1-0 ⚪️ 75' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Yet another chance for City, as Yearn is denied brilliantly by Grainger from close range.

1-0 ⚪️ 71' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻
RT @DulwichHamletFC: SUB: Johl Powell replaced Andre Blackman (68') https://t.co/O5DhScgfdO

A rare chance for the hosts in the second-half as substitute Mills proves a problem for the City defence, before firing well over in the box.

1-0 ⚪️ 66' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Double change for City!

1-0 ⚪️ 63' #TheClarets https://t.co/BBj3WUoSVs

Now Jackson heads over from Dunne's cross! So many chances, the Clarets are pushing!

1-0 ⚪️ 63' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻
RT @DulwichHamletFC: SUB: Danny Mills replaced Nana Owusu (62') https://t.co/O5DhScgfdO

The chances keep coming for City! Jackson drives at the Dulwich defence before taking aim, which is deflected just over the bar!

Winfield then sees a header from the resulting corner saved well by Grainger!

1-0 ⚪️ 61' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Another City chance... Trotter's ball into the box is met by Lodovica, who on the turn, sees his shot blocked and eventually collected by Grainger.

1-0 ⚪️ 55' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE!

We should be level here... Yearn's corner finds Winfield unmarked in the box, but the towering defender heads wide!

1-0 ⚪️ 50' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

We're back underway. Come on, you Clarets!!

1-0 ⚪️ 46' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻
Behind at the break.

Dulwich's Porter receives a booking for throwing the ball away after conceding a foul on Vaz. 

1-0 ⚪️ 45+3' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE!

Esan shows some great skill to keep the ball under pressure, before teeing up Dunne nicely for a shot, as the ball whistles just wide!

1-0 ⚪️ 44' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

City really pushing and looking for an equaliser before half-time.

Keep going guys!

1-0 ⚪️ 42' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE AGAIN!

A series of corners for City as Trotter has a header first saved by Grainger, and another header go wide! So, so close...

1-0 ⚪️ 37' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

CLOSE! A City corner causes havoc in the Dulwich box as Lodovica eventually sees his headed effort cleared off the line!

James and Ming then receive a yellow for a coming together in the box.

1-0 ⚪️ 36' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

It's been a bit of a scrappy game so far this evening, but the Clarets are pushing for an equaliser.

1-0 ⚪️ 32' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

ALMOST AN INSTANT RESPONSE!

Vaz's deflected cross is met by Lodovica, as Grainger saves his initial shot, before somehow saving again from Jackson's followup!

1-0 ⚪️ 21' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Goal for Dulwich. The hosts have continued to press and look dangerous from kick-off and Clarke fires them into the lead with a low shot past Ejeheri.

1-0 ⚪️ 19' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Winfield receives the games first booking for a foul, preventing the hosts from breaking on the counter.

0-0 ⚪️ 11' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Another early chance for Dulwich as this time Felix has space to force Ejeheri into a good save.

0-0 ⚪️ 5' #TheClarets

Click the link below to listen live ⬇️📻

Early chance for the hosts as a long ball over the top of the City defence allows Porter to get a shot off at goal, which Ejeheri is equal to to deny the attacker.

0-0 ⚪️ 4' #TheClarets
